grade_evaluation.et:
1. Osalemine tundides vähemalt 80% ulatuses (lubatud 5 puudumist; 6-7 puudumise korral tuleb kirjutada arvestuslik test, mille tulemus peab olema rohkem kui 51%, kui puudumisi on 8 või rohkem, on kursus mittearvestatud. 
2. kontrolltööde (3) sooritamine positiivsele hindele (vähemalt 51% õigeid vastuseid);
3. tekstid (4) ja helifailid on arvestatud;


In order to get a positive result at the end of the semester, you need to fill in ALL these requirements:
1) participate in the course;
5 absences are allowed. If one has 6-7 absences, one must write the final exam which must be positively graded. If one has 8 or more absences, the result will be F or not-present.
2) pass 3 coverage tests (result is 51% or more);
3) write 4 texts which are positively graded; 
4) record 2 audiofiles together with a partner, audiofiles are positively graded. 

Please note that one can not retake the test that already has a positive result.
If one needs to retake the test, then the result is the average of these two results.
Tests can be rewritten only once.
